# Whitelist: upload only the dashboard artefact, the API function (and its specific
# runtime dependencies), and platform config. Credentials, raw caches, and everything
# else in "source datasets" (Master List, Site Verification, IOM submissions, maps)
# never leave this machine via Vercel regardless of what appears in this folder later.
*
!public
!public/**
!vercel.json
!api
!api/**
api/__pycache__
!requirements.txt

# api/operational.py's own runtime dependencies — nothing broader than this.
!live_fetch.py
!build_operational.py
!build_dashboard_from_live_data.py
!zite_map.json
!data
!data/xlsform.xlsx
